=head3 OnSegv()

Request a trace back followed by exit on a B<segv> signal.


B<Example:>



    OnSegv();                                                                   # Request a trace back followed by exit on a segv signal.  # 𝗘𝘅𝗮𝗺𝗽𝗹𝗲


